    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3463" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3636" key="#Principissa">Garetrude</persName> dilecte
                        coniugis nostre, tibi <name ref="Autulus">Autulo</name>
                        <rs key="#Gold #Specialized_workers">aurifici</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >integras res</rs> que fuit <name ref="Mundulus">Munduli</name> et <name
                            ref="Ibbrulus">Ibbruli</name>
                        <rs key="#Slave">servi</rs> sacri nostri <rs key="#Palatium">palatii</rs> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            >Folianense</placeName>, quas <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi homines</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">sine preceptum
                            tenunt</rs> per annos quindecim et ipsi servis defuncti sunt; pertinet
                        ex <rs key="#Marepahis">mariparsato</rs> predicte coniugis nostre; in ea
                        videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum
                        predictas res tu et heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod
                        vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione superius dictii potestatis uti
                        prelegitur scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3637"
                            >Benedictus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> septimo anno, mense octubrio,
                        nona indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
